  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4485858/" class="title-link">梁家有训三达德</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4485858"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/suyunxin/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1374591-140.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/suyunxin/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">蓝文青</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-11-24"
      class="main-meta">2010-11-24 21:50:26</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4485858_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  提倡“百善孝为先”的中国，从蒙学的《朱子家训》，《颜氏家训》，一直到清末的《曾国藩家训》，任何一篇关于教导自己子女立身、处世、做学问的文章，都有一副神色严峻的教训面孔，板着，端着，让孩子和家人觉得惧怕。  有此印象，对于写这类文章的父亲们，便都有了一种固定的...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4485858/#comments">(16回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">47有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4485858_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4485858_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
